					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"The President of the Disciplinary Committee always makes it through somehow. That’s just how it is.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"FS的风纪委员长或许很适合那种人也说不定。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"FS的風紀委員長或許很適合那種人也說不定。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0076_00059",
